---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 306
      - text: "我只能说，不愧是我的好妹妹……\n这样你就能更为熟练地使用达尔克尔的守护了！"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 312
      - text: "如果见到了盖侬那混蛋，你替我转告它。\n就说“永别了，盖侬……”。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 154
      - text: "妹妹！\n你又来测试自己的本领了！？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 257
      - text: "嗯，现在的你……\n要对付灾厄盖侬的话，简直易如反掌啊！"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 164
      - text: "妹妹！你能帮我把一些话\n转告给那个年轻人吗？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 356
      - text: "你告诉他，我小时候被人叫做阿达。\n胆子比他还要小3倍。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 270
      - text: "但只要肯努力工作，能为同伴着想，\n并且经常啃食美味的岩石，你就可以变强……"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 139
      - text: 如果你能这样告诉他的话，兄弟我感激不尽……
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 211
      - text: "妹妹！你还记得我们\n第一次见面时的事情吗？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 251
      - text: "当时我怎么都不会想到，海利亚人当中\n竟然会有能让我叫“妹妹”的强者存在……"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 323
      - text: "难道你忘了我当时那副\n呆若木鸡的表情了吗……？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 226
      - text: "那个，妹妹。\n看来你的记忆好像还很混乱……"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 241
      - text: "或许你可以去读一下那东西。\n那上面写有你我相遇时的事情。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 275
      - text: "那东西就是我以前写的日记。\n现在它应该还在什么地方。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 252
      - text: "看来我写日记这事让你感到很意外呢。\n不过，你就去找找看吧。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 190
      - text: "妹妹！你听好了啊。\n接下来我说的话你绝不能告诉其他人。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 243
      - text: "这事我只告诉你一人。\n其实有个怪物我怎么也打不赢它。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 262
      - text: "当我还小的时候，有一次我踩到了它的尾巴。\n它嗷呜一声后，立刻“汪”地叫了一声，\n然后就发出“呜噜噜”的声音。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 321
      - text: "它狗牙咧嘴……不，龇牙咧嘴的样子\n直到今天还让我心里毛毛的。"
